239
00:21:45,080 --> 00:21:47,320
Bayangkan jika kau bersamanya.

240
00:21:47,360 --> 00:21:50,760
Itu akan seperti putri cantik
dan pangeran kodok.

241
00:21:51,880 --> 00:21:54,800
Itu sangat lucu.

242
00:21:56,520 --> 00:21:58,361
